summary: Play as Lisette, the Breton female of Solitude !!!
descriptionHtml:
Still don\'t look quite as well as the original Lisette, but is the closest I could got her of similarity. I put a warpaint on her face and her libs on red and some shadow on her eyes to make her look not so pale ^_^ !!. Game progress is on River wood after scaping Alduin\'s attack and ready to go to Whiterun Kingdom !! Wearing Imperial outfit and carrying 5077 gold (enough to buy your first house in Whiterun). 

Hope you like it, any suggestion is welcome :3 !!
Merry Christmas !!!
